name: Un-Counted Bags Report
query:
select t1.name as "Bag Number:Link/Collection Entry:100", 
t1.machine_number as "Machine Numer:Link/Asset:100", 
t1.site as "Site: Link/Warehouse: 100" from `tabCollection Entry` t1
left join `tabCollection Counting` t2 on t2.collection_entry = t1.name
where t2.name IS NULL and t1.entry_type = "Collection Entry"
